</pdd.agentic_langtest>

# Deliverables
A single file `pdd/get_test_command.py` exposing the `TestCommand` dataclass, `get_test_command_for_file`, `_detect_ts_test_runner`, and `_load_language_format` (locating `language_format.csv` under package-relative or project-root-relative `data/`), plus whatever internal helpers the contract requires. All paths handled via `pathlib`.
